{
  "stem": "12491.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were just running the camp like the camp was run before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were distributing food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the 28 people, maybe they got some additional help-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was within the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very few people dared to get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to remember that we were close to Sudetenland, which was actually a German population.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were kind of afraid of going in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We did go there eventually, in a very strong force, when the Russians arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Eventually, the Russian administration came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They registered everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They started to make preparations for repatriation to Poland, to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this took several weeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the meantime, we got acquainted with some of the Russian officers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One of them was a Jewish lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he, and several people-- I never was part of it, unfortunately, I wish I would be-- I would have been-- they went into the Sudetenland villages and they got into the German homes and simply took away whatever they thought would be needed by our people.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is how I got my first suit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Two sizes oversized, but it was my first-- I didn't-- I did not have to wear my striped suit anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Eventually, some weeks after that-- after we had distributed the fabrics to the-- to everybody and everything else-- a train arrived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were loaded up into the train and taken to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Since most of the railroad tracks were broken, we knew that it would take several days, even though it wasn't such a great, long distance.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we equipped all the wagons with-- this was all transport railroad-- we equipped it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We took our bunk beds in them, put them in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we took little stove, iron stove, and then we cooked.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
